data.description: What?!? You just HAVE to see this marvel! Over 47 ACRES of totally fenced in beautiful ranch land with a SPACIOUS log cabin-style home AND a guest cottage. This one-of-a-kind property comes with a HUGE metal shop, garage, large carport, storage buildings, in-ground pool, sauna, hot tub, deer blind, deer feeding station, and hog pen. This wonderful ranch is ready for your year-round enjoyment and perfect for the Texas lifestyle.
